An add-on that adds new furniture, with great variations and possibilities!
With tables that you can mold to your taste, and more!In addition to furniture that has interactions!
Enjoy!
This is the NEW ERA OF PEEPSSS FURNITURE!

Looking for a beautiful and modern furniture addon?
Youre in the right place!Loled Furniture adds over 100 blocks and several of these blocks are functional!

This add-on adds many decorations, furniture, more villagers.

There is everything from kitchen utensils and bathroom equipment to things like a stove, shower products and entertainment-related things, like a pool table and a PC for games.

It is a great addon if you want more options to decorate your home.

FurniDeco adds 25 pieces of functional, decorative and unique-looking furniture that fit with the vanilla style.

With more than 80 variants in total, FurniDeco gives you endless options to furniture & decorate your builds!Features:- 25 Unique pieces of furniture & decorations, up to 80+ variants- Fully customizable- Interactive and functional- Fits with the Minecraft Vanilla feel- Craft-able in survival mode- Uses blocks

Do you want to decorate your medieval houses but you can't do it with the game blocks?This addon adds many new blocks with 3D models to create epic decorations.

 Now supports resource packsThis addon adds many new blocks with all types of wood and is compatible with resource packs.

 All the 3D models were created by me and I used some Minecraft textures for some blocks.

 With these blocks they can decorate many places in their medieval houses.

This is a really great addon which includes 20+ different furniture.

Each furniture has a different use such as sitting or some kind of interaction (e.

g.

storage or trading).

For example, the radio can be used for playing songs and the fridge can be used for storing food items.

But the main and most important part is the fact that they look really good and can also be used just as decorations for your builds.

Modern Furniture is a decoration add-on prepared both for a survival world and for a creative game.

The addon brings more than 270 furniture with color variants and much more!
